{"id": "art-4711", "label": "Art. 4711", "title": "Art. 4711: Registrul Unic al Transparenţei Intereselor (RUTI)", "slug": "art-4711", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_751003165\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1660\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_751003165\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><u><span style='color:#569748'>Art. 47<sup>11</sup>:\nRegistrul Unic al Transparen&#355;ei Intereselor (RUTI) </span></u></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_320799245\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1659\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_320799245\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(1)Secretariatul General al Guvernului administreaz&#259;\nRegistrul Unic al Transparen&#355;ei Intereselor, www.ruti.gov.ro, denumit în\ncontinuare RUTI, sub forma unei platforme publice, accesibil&#259; online,\npentru a asigura transparen&#355;a activit&#259;&#355;ilor ce pot\ninfluen&#355;a luarea unei decizii, reprezentând un cadru de colaborare\ncomplementar &#351;i anterior procedurii legale de transparen&#355;&#259;\ndecizional&#259;.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_769888158\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1658\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_769888158\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(2)În în&#355;elesul prezentului capitol, prin persoane\nter&#355;e se în&#355;elege orice reprezentant al unei societ&#259;&#355;i cu\npersonalitate juridic&#259;, asocia&#355;ie, funda&#355;ie, federa&#355;ie,\norganiza&#355;ie religioas&#259;/a cultelor sau asociat&#259; unui cult,\norganiza&#355;ie sindical&#259;, organiza&#355;ie patronal&#259;, camer&#259;\nde comer&#355;, structur&#259; asociativ&#259; a administra&#355;iei publice\nlocale, alte tipuri de organiza&#355;ii legal constituite, persoan&#259;\nfizic&#259; autorizat&#259;, întreprindere individual&#259;, întreprindere\nfamilial&#259;, cabinet individual, cabinet asociat, societate\nprofesional&#259;, grupurile de interes economic, cu sau f&#259;r&#259;\npersonalitate juridic&#259;, sau orice grup/re&#355;ea oficial&#259; sau\ninformal&#259; care are un interes pentru un anumit domeniu ce intr&#259; în\ncompeten&#355;a de reglementare a unei institu&#355;ii &#351;i\nautorit&#259;&#355;i publice centrale.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2114655109\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1657\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2114655109\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(3)Persoanele prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup> alin.\n(1) au obliga&#355;ia de a se înregistra în RUTI &#351;i de a publica\nîntâlnirile oficiale cu persoane ter&#355;e cu cel pu&#355;in dou&#259; zile\nînaintea desf&#259;&#351;ur&#259;rii acestora.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1009938351\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1656\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1009938351\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Întâlnirile\noficiale publicate în RUTI includ urm&#259;toarele informa&#355;ii:</b></span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2008088596\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1655\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2008088596\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>a)numele persoanelor &#351;i/sau denumirea\nentit&#259;&#355;ilor participante;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_845055226\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1654\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_845055226\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>b)data &#351;i locul întâlnirii;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_162638798\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1653\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_162638798\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>c)descrierea scopului întâlnirii.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1829901052\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1652\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1829901052\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(5)În termen de 5 zile lucr&#259;toare de la\ndesf&#259;&#351;urarea întâlnirii prev&#259;zute la alin. (3),\ninforma&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (4) vor fi completate cu principalele\nteme de discu&#355;ie &#351;i concluziile acestora, dup&#259; caz.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_609897681\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1651\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_609897681\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(6)Persoanele prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup> alin.\n(1) pot solicita înregistrarea în RUTI a persoanelor ter&#355;e în vederea\nparticip&#259;rii la întâlnirile oficiale.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_873386276\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1650\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_873386276\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(7)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Prin\nexcep&#355;ie de la prevederile alin. (3), persoanele prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup>\nalin. (1) nu public&#259; întâlnirile oficiale care au ca obiect:</b></span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1719901041\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1649\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1719901041\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>a)dreptul unei persoane fizice de a beneficia de servicii\npublice sau dreptul s&#259;u la via&#355;&#259; privat&#259; garantat de lege;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1011370548\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1648\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1011370548\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>b)reprezentarea drepturilor legale ale unei\np&#259;r&#355;i sau ale unui participant implicat într-un proces administrativ\nsau judiciar, în contextul respectivelor proceduri;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1393138811\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1647\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1393138811\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>c)reprezentarea intereselor de politic&#259; extern&#259;\nîn rela&#355;iile diplomatice sau consulare;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_34297249\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1646\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_34297249\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>d)comunic&#259;rile care fac parte din\nreglement&#259;rile privind condi&#355;iile de munc&#259; &#351;i de încadrare\nîn munc&#259; sau care sunt direct legate de acestea, întreprinse de\nreprezentan&#355;ii unui sindicat în numele membrilor s&#259;i;</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_860696787\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1645\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_860696787\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>e)informa&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 12 din Legea\nnr. 544/2001 privind liberul acces la informa&#355;iile de interes public, cu\nmodific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile ulterioare.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_60905909\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1644\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_60905909\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(8)Persoanele prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup> alin.\n(1) au obliga&#355;ia de a publica întâlnirile oficiale cu persoane ter&#355;e,\ncare s-au desf&#259;&#351;urat f&#259;r&#259; o planificare prealabil&#259;, în\ntermen de dou&#259; zile de la data desf&#259;&#351;ur&#259;rii acestora.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_954293117\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1643\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_954293117\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(9)Persoanele cu rang de demnitar din cadrul\nautorit&#259;&#355;ilor administrative autonome, prefec&#355;ii,\nsubprefec&#355;ii &#351;i autorit&#259;&#355;ile administra&#355;iei publice\nlocale pot solicita înregistrarea în RUTI &#351;i pot publica întâlnirile\noficiale cu persoane ter&#355;e, în condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin.\n(3)-(8).</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_199836079\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1642\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_199836079\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(10)Gestionarea RUTI se realizeaz&#259; cu respectarea\nRegulamentului (UE) 2016/679 al Parlamentului European &#351;i al Consiliului\ndin 27 aprilie 2016 privind protec&#355;ia persoanelor fizice în ceea ce\nprive&#351;te prelucrarea datelor cu caracter personal &#351;i privind libera\ncircula&#355;ie a acestor date &#351;i de abrogare a Directivei 95/46/CE\n(Regulamentul general privind protec&#355;ia datelor), a Legii nr. 190/2018\nprivind m&#259;suri de punere în aplicare a Regulamentului (UE) 2016/679 al\nParlamentului European &#351;i al Consiliului din 27 aprilie 2016 privind\nprotec&#355;ia persoanelor fizice în ceea ce prive&#351;te prelucrarea datelor\ncu caracter personal &#351;i privind libera circula&#355;ie a acestor date\n&#351;i de abrogare a Directivei 95/46/CE (Regulamentul general privind protec&#355;ia\ndatelor), cu modific&#259;rile ulterioare, precum &#351;i a legisla&#355;iei\nna&#355;ionale privind domeniul protec&#355;iei datelor cu caracter personal.</span></u></p>"}